dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"4&gt;3&gt;6=5&gt;2&gt;7&gt;1<br />\n<br />\n8未睇"},{"pid":"45e6c4698bcd0019c316c80e886d2cf755ee5e9c","tid":2517414,"uid":205394,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:18:29.000Z","msg":"JoJo係一部好睇角色魅力既作品<br />\n<br />\n個主線幾乎簡單到唔簡單<br />\n故事性幾乎係靠一場又一場既遭遇戰去串連<br />\n但係佢就係咁撚勁<br />\n連出場一次就死既角色都可以成為經典<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\nSBR唔係<br />\n佢係連故事性都兼顧埋<br />\n而且有認真想去培養一個角色既心理成長<br />\n真係無撚得輸<br />\n<br />\n遭遇戰同角色魅力仍有保留<br />\n但係雙主角既成長同主線都好精彩<br />\n<br />\n而且SBR重好著重，都係之前幾部無既要素<br />\n好似最撚經典既雪中乾杯<br />\n<br />\n荒木拎出SBR真係證明左<br />\n除左角色魅力<br />\n佢都可以寫出一部好有深度好有意境既好故事<br />\n<br />\nBut <br />\n設定上既bug重係佢改唔到既壞習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但睇開jojo既人都會接受呢點"},{"pid":"4d1344e6e58b58b2411d1fb29721893e3d47d6f6","tid":2517414,"uid":43613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"7&gt;&gt;6=2&gt;4&gt;5&gt;&gt;3&gt;1"},{"pid":"12a18038849300ad08d184db7775fbcdec9d8375","tid":2517414,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761e590e443fa40d75361fc417e47ce1a0b2b5b1","tid":2517414,"uid":461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"好似冇人同我一樣覺得第三部最好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:35:51.000Z","msg":"第三部最多笑位<br />\n最鍾意兩兄弟嗰兩集<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b741f99b3b9163862619e4169aefca3058a55d91","tid":2517414,"uid":60728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:39:25.000Z","msg":"7 &gt; 6 &gt; 4 &gt; 5 &gt; 2 &gt; 3 &gt; 1<br />\n<br />\n其實2好好睇 不過頭兩部好難擺埋一齊比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e9f605e05a1865f86792dbe27181280b532aca","tid":2517414,"uid":374353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu